==Yin Fire Snake (丁巳)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊}}), the month of {{ill|April|ja|4月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Teishi|ja|丁巳}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Old Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Summer|ja|立夏}} until the day before {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種}}) as applicable.

==Yin Fire Snake (丁巳)'s Days==
=== 選日 ===
The selected day for {{ill|Teishi|ja|丁巳}} is the 4th day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専}} (excluding gap days).

