A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 57 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Teishi|ja|丁巳|12=draft|12=draft}}.
