==Yin Fire Snake (丁巳)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|April|ja|4月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}} of {{ill|Teishi|ja|1=Yin Fire Snake|2=ja|丁巳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teishi|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Summer|ja|立夏|1=Lixia|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Summer|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mangzhong|qq=}}) as applicable.

==Yin Fire Snake (丁巳)'s Days==
=== 選日 ===
The selected day for {{ill|Teishi|ja|1=Yin Fire Snake|2=ja|丁巳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teishi|qq=}} is the 4th day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}} (excluding gap days).

