==Yin Fire Snake (丁巳)'s Months== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|lt=Mizunoto (癸)|2=ja|3=癸|4=zh|5=癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|lt=Tsuchinoe (戊)|2=ja|3=戊|4=zh|5=戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:April|April]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|month (calendar)]] of {{ill|Teishi|ja|1=Yin Fire Snake|2=ja|丁巳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teishi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teishi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Snake|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Lixia|Lixia]] until the day before [[:en:Mangzhong|Mangzhong]]) as applicable.
==Yin Fire Snake (丁巳)'s Days== === 選日 === The selected day for {{ill|Teishi|ja|1=Yin Fire Snake|2=ja|丁巳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teishi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teishi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Snake|qq=}} is the 4th day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}} (excluding gap days).
